readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to retrieve a VAC2 invoice attachment and details to be sent to the applicant with a cover letter in order for the applicant to make the VAC2 payment online.

Service Behaviour

VAC2 Payment requested event is created in ICSE, ICSE calls ECS (SV322) with the details required for ECS to call SAP with this service.
This service will retrieve the VAC2 invoice attachment and details from SAP to send to the applicant with a cover letter in order for the applicant to make the VAC2 payment online.
